data.description: This wonderful upgraded large home is a deal, room for lots of people, can be good for an airbnb. Has a large family room with wood burning stove and large living room with large dinning area in between and upgraded appliances in large kitchen with lots of storage. This home is great for entertainment , has a long drive way for parking and circular driveway in front, home is on city sewer, 2 sheds for storage and a dog run on one side of home. Home has 3 bedrooms and 2 baths and 4 bonus rooms (use your imagination for usages), new toilets , new walk in shower in master bath, Newer roof, and newer floors. Make this home a must see.
